creator: Ian Cosgrove
descriptionHtml:
St Peter’s Swim School is proud to present our fantastic Parent Portal booking system in App form directly to your mobile device.

The St Peter’s Swim School Parent Portal App will help you manage your entire family’s swimming schedules in one place. Loaded with easy-to-use features our Parent Portal App allows you to:

Manage student attendance and absences, and book make-up lessons
Request class changes and book new classes
Monitor student progress with assessment histories and skill evaluation information
Maintain family payment and student enrolment information
Our Parent Portal App will also notify you of any news and announcements directly to your device.

Download the St Peter’s Swim School Parent Portal App today. Available at the App Store and Google Play or scan the QR code below to begin the download.
